  <title>错误框</title>
      <p>
          Use the <cmd>--error</cmd> option to create an error dialog.  
      </p>

      <p>
        The following example script shows how to create an error dialog:
      </p>

<code>
#!/bin/bash

zenity --error \
--text="Could not find /var/log/syslog."
</code>


